{"tid":1154410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有個方法，可以收番新移民嘅公屋。","createTime":"2019-05-14T09:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T09:33:07.000Z","uid":189799,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f588d1c35f579c9457e1062d1cf4f316beec4cc3","tid":1154410,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"根據政策，如果公屋住戶衰以下其中一樣就會比人收屋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/14/172630_1bc9960986aed46d174816f53624b81d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F14%2F172630_1bc9960986aed46d174816f53624b81d.jpg&h=47582e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講，係第一項先易啲捉到。所以如果你係住梗公屋，而你鄰居係新移民。麻煩留意下佢地係咪成日唔見人（最少1個月）。係就去投訴。因為有啲大陸人攞完公屋，就返番大陸。<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係咁容易收屋，但20單有1單都好。好過做鍵盤戰士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ObbRFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ObbRFh.jpg&h=bb23fe6a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}